text: Mimozethes is a genus of moths belonging to the subfamily Cyclidiinae. It was first described by Warren in 1901. ==Species== * Mimozethes angula Chu & Wang, 1987 * Mimozethes argentilinearia Leech, 1897 * Mimozethes lilacinaria Leech, 1897 ==References== Category:Cyclidiinae Category:Drepanidae genera
title: Mimozethes
